## ── Production (Makefile output) ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# `make up` copies the built Vite SPA into BannerShop.Api/wwwroot/ before
# publishing. The folder itself is kept (with .gitkeep), but built artifacts
# must not be committed.
BannerShop.Api/wwwroot/*
!BannerShop.Api/wwwroot/.gitkeep
# Generated by `make up` if the user ever copies the file back to the source
# tree; contains the embedded DB password & JWT secret.
BannerShop.Api/appsettings.Production.json

